reviewText: The most concise, informative,well documented and educational videos that won't bore you; because they are so riveting with information and so well narrated + put together, well no review could do them justice, a must have if your any fan of history and how things actually take place in this civilized world?????
Gift for my husband, who is a WWI/WWII history buff.  He really enjoys being able to watch the episodes w/o all those commercials!  Very well packaged and arrived in a timely fashion.
